        <abstract>
            <p>Discusses American Negroes and their parasitic lice. Henry Denny’s need for lice specimens.</p>
            <p>Discusses effects of racial crosses in man.</p>
            <p>Describes his trip to Yorkshire.</p> 
<p>Comments on Sedgwick’s review [of <hi rend="italic">Vestiges of creation</hi>].</p>  
<p>Mentions Humboldt’s <hi rend="italic">Kosmos</hi>. Criticises Humboldt’s geology.</p> 
        </abstract>
